dc_title_s: South America, Venezuela, Cumaná to Picuda Grande (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. "From a survey by U.S.S. Hannibal in 1938 and 1939 in collaboration with the Venezuelan Government." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Map no.24433. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
